org.apache.jena.sparql.core

Interface TransactionalComponent


  • public interface TransactionalComponent
    Interface that encapsulates the transaction lifecycle for a component in a transaction. This is the system interface. Transactional is the application view of a set of collection of components that together provide transactions.
